      <vspace*|1fn><with|font-series|<quote|bold>|math-font-series|<quote|bold>|2<space|2spc>短文本><datoms|<macro|x|<repeat|<arg|x>|<with|font-series|medium|<with|font-size|1|<space|0.05fn>.<space|0.05fn>>>>>|<htab|5mm>><no-break><pageref|auto-2><vspace|0.5fn>

      <vspace*|1fn><with|font-series|<quote|bold>|math-font-series|<quote|bold>|3<space|2spc>多行文本块><datoms|<macro|x|<repeat|<arg|x>|<with|font-series|medium|<with|font-size|1|<space|0.05fn>.<space|0.05fn>>>>>|<htab|5mm>><no-break><pageref|auto-3><vspace|0.5fn>

